<title type="html"><![CDATA[4/3(Sat.)Cell therapy to give fresh hope to cancer sufferers/Traffic accidents claimed eight lives a day(Host: James)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=486&amp;p=508#p508"><![CDATA[
4/3(Sat.)Cell therapy to give fresh hope to cancer sufferers/Traffic accidents claimed eight lives a day last year(Host: James)<br /><br /><br />Article1: Cell therapy to give fresh hope to cancer sufferers<br /><a href="https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2019/02/13/2003709664?utm_medium=P" class="postlink">https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2019/02/13/2003709664?utm_medium=P</a><br /><br />Question:<br />1. Have you ever heard of cell therapy? How about the cure rate to use it;<br />2. Have you ever heard of your friends or relatives got cancer? What kind of methods they defeat it;<br />3. How to prevent from getting cancer? What’s your suggestion?<br />4. Besides cancer or stroke, what kind of deceased is the most common in Taiwan, How to prevent it ?<br /><br />Article2: Traffic accidents claimed eight lives a day last year<br /><a href="https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2020/03/31/2003733713" class="postlink">https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2020/03/31/2003733713</a><br /><br />Question:<br />1. What’s your commute vehicles to go outside ？ Do you feel it’s safe?<br />2. What kind of innovation you have to prevent pedestrians across the road ignored traffic lights.<br />3. How to manage senior citizens to prevent them from accident?<br />4. Do you feel MRT safer than other vehicles? <br /><br /><br />///////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔！<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1000元 (學生:500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Tue Mar 30, 2021 10:17 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
